            </t>
            <t id="" hasRuby="0" time="" torder="1" index="41" vertical="0">
                <start-time>00:02:13,750</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:15,750</end-time>
                <translation>这是德语</translation>
                <original>これドイツ語でございまして</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t id="" hasRuby="0" time="" torder="1" index="42" vertical="0">
                <start-time>00:02:15,750</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:18,571</end-time>
                <translation>由两个词组合而成的</translation>
                <original>２つの言葉を掛け合わせた言葉なんですね</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t id="" hasRuby="0" time="" torder="1" index="43" vertical="0">
                <start-time>00:02:18,571</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:22,470</end-time>
                <translation>前半部分的“Bildung”意为形成、成长</translation>
                <original>前半のビルディングっていうのは形成・成長</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t id="" hasRuby="0" time="" torder="1" index="44" vertical="0">
                <start-time>00:02:22,470</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:25,070</end-time>
                <translation>后半部分的“Roman”则是小说……的意思</translation>
                <original>で後半の｢ロマン｣が小説と…っていう意味合いで</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t id="" hasRuby="0" time="" torder="1" index="45" vertical="0">
                <start-time>00:02:25,100</start-time>
                <end-time>00:02:27,275</end-time>
