            </t>
            <t id="" hasRuby="0" time="" torder="1" index="451" vertical="0">
                <start-time>00:22:06,558</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:08,300</end-time>
                <translation>故事不会以皆大欢喜的结局收场</translation>
                <original>めでたしめでたしにはならないのは</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t id="" hasRuby="0" time="" torder="1" index="452" vertical="0">
                <start-time>00:22:08,300</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:10,893</end-time>
                <translation>这一点已经毫无疑问 非常清楚了</translation>
                <original>もう間違いなくよく分かりますけど</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t id="" hasRuby="0" time="" torder="1" index="453" vertical="0">
                <start-time>00:22:10,893</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:12,860</end-time>
                <translation>但正因为它没有过于强调这一点</translation>
                <original>そこが強すぎないから</original>
