            </t>
            <t id="" hasRuby="0" time="" torder="1" index="455" vertical="0">
                <start-time>00:22:14,849</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:19,371</end-time>
                <translation>这大概会持续地吸引读者的兴趣</translation>
                <original>興味を引き続けるだろうなというのは感じます</original>
