                <start-time>00:22:31,583</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:32,884</end-time>
                <translation>就是在这样一个时代</translation>
                <original>っていう時代で</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t id="" hasRuby="0" time="" torder="1" index="461" vertical="0">
                <start-time>00:22:32,884</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:34,286</end-time>
                <translation>在工人阶级内部
この労働者階級の中にも</translation>
                <original/>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t id="" hasRuby="0" time="" torder="1" index="462" vertical="0">
                <start-time>00:22:34,286</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:36,692</end-time>
                <translation>能够读书写字的人群也逐渐增多</translation>
                <original>今度読み書きのできる層というのが増えていくと</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t id="" hasRuby="0" time="" torder="1" index="463" vertical="0">
                <start-time>00:22:36,692</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:38,554</end-time>
                <translation>对于这些新读者来说</translation>
                <original>こういった新しい読者にとって</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t id="" hasRuby="0" time="" torder="1" index="464" vertical="0">
                <start-time>00:22:38,554</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:41,978</end-time>
                <translation>狄更斯这种捕捉时代潮流而创作的作品</translation>
                <original>この時流をキャッチして書いたディケンズ作品というのは</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t id="" hasRuby="0" time="" torder="1" index="465" vertical="0">
                <start-time>00:22:41,978</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:43,595</end-time>
                <translation>用我们现在的感觉来说就是</translation>
                <original>我々の感覚でいうと</original>
                <spell/>
            </t>
            <t id="" hasRuby="0" time="" torder="1" index="466" vertical="0">
                <start-time>00:22:43,595</start-time>
                <end-time>00:22:45,535</end-time>
                <translation>就像看电视剧一样</translation>
