            <t id="" hasRuby="0" time="" torder="1" index="474" vertical="0">
                <start-time>00:23:03,521</start-time>
                <end-time>00:23:05,684</end-time>
                <translation>而这一点 与皮普所生活的社会</translation>
                <original>それとピップが生きた社会</original>
